<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The system Clock. </para>



<para>Normally only one instance of that clock is created per application. It manages and synchronizes multiple Alarm objects that each are responsible to manage the time periodic triggering of a specific Task <?linebreak?> </para>
</section>
